name: 50 Web Sign up/log in designs
description:
We pretty much use sign up/log in to websites/apps on a daily basis.

-----------------------------------------------------

Hope this pack of 50 common sign up/log in design patterns to inspire your next project.

⭐︎ Auto-layout

⭐︎ Customizable with text, colors, images, icons...

⭐︎ Made with Figma and an open resources

-----------------------------------------------------

Please feel free to remix this with your own designs and add more explorations. Please tag me if you would like to do a remix. Enjoy and have fun with it! Thank you ^_^!
